<li>Farias (1 differences)
<ul>
<li>Farias (MDD) vs. Tomas Hrbek (unchecked; unspecified) (tried: Hrbek, T. Hrbek) (Hesperomys) (MDD#1000802; <a href="https://hesperomys.com/t/58544">Mico munduruku</a>; Author 3; original citation: <a href="https://hesperomys.com/a/51980">Costa-Araújo et al. (2019)</a>; authority)</li>
</ul></li>
<li>Hrbek (1 differences)
<ul>
<li>Hrbek (MDD) vs. Izeni Pires Farias (unchecked; unspecified) (tried: Farias, I. Farias, I. P. Farias, I. Pires Farias, I.P. Farias) (Hesperomys) (MDD#1000802; <a href="https://hesperomys.com/t/58544">Mico munduruku</a>; Author 2; original citation: <a href="https://hesperomys.com/a/51980">Costa-Araújo et al. (2019)</a>; authority)</li>
<li>The authors for the name are given as “R Costa-Araújo, IP Farias &amp; T Hrbek”; MDD switches the order of the last two</li>
</ul></li>
