<li>L. F. Oliveira (MDD) vs. Luiz Flamarion Barbosa de Oliveira (Brazilian mammalogist; checked; portuguese) (tried: L. F. B. Oliveira, L. F. B. de Oliveira, L. Oliveira, L. de Oliveira, L.F.B. Oliveira, L.F.B. de Oliveira, Oliveira, de Oliveira) (Hesperomys) (MDD#1002471; <a href="https://hesperomys.com/t/32451">Scapteromys meridionalis</a>; Author 5; original citation: <a href="https://hesperomys.com/a/18709">Quintela et al. (2014)</a>; authority)</li>
