</ul></li>
<li>L. von Bohmann (3 differences)
<ul>
<li>L. von Bohmann (MDD) vs. Ludwig Bohmann (unchecked; german) (tried: Bohmann, L. Bohmann) (Hesperomys) (MDD#1006575; <a href="https://hesperomys.com/t/63080">Dendromus kumasi</a>; Author 1; authority)</li>
