<li>Pontes (1 differences)
<ul>
<li>Pontes (MDD) vs. Antonio Rossano Mendes Pontes (unchecked; general) (tried: A. Mendes Pontes, A. R. Mendes Pontes, A. Rossano Mendes Pontes, A.R. Mendes Pontes, Mendes Pontes) (Hesperomys) (MDD#1001251; <a href="https://hesperomys.com/t/33843">Coendou speratus</a>; Author 1; original citation: <a href="https://hesperomys.com/a/12236">Mendes Pontes et al. (2013)</a>; authority)</li>
<li>Within the <em>Coendou speratus</em> article several previous papers by the same authors are cited as “Mendes Pontes et al.”, so I think the family name is “Mendes Pontes”.</li>
</ul></li>
<li>Páez (1 differences)
<ul>
<li>Páez (MDD) vs. Fredy A. Rivera-Páez (unchecked; spanish) (tried: F. A. Rivera-Páez, F. Rivera-Páez, F.A. Rivera-Páez, Rivera-Páez) (Hesperomys) (MDD#1006597; <a href="https://hesperomys.com/t/59193">Eptesicus orinocensis</a>; Author 8; original citation: <a href="https://hesperomys.com/a/56583">Ramírez-Chaves et al. (2021)</a>; authority)</li>
<li>He also named <em>Eptesicus langeri</em> and there you have him as “Rivera-Páez” already; would prefer to use that spelling in both cases.</li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
